page.title: 12Visitors to South Park
page.content: The site at South Park is woodland and heathland.Most of the area is open with much greenery. Three visitors to the park were interviewed.They stated that they used the area to walk their dogs or to stroll.All three interviewed stated that they were locals,living no more than seven miles away.Each of them said that they liked this particular site,although one stated that she did not use the site regularly.One also said that she preferred to use the site three miles away,but the other two stated that they preferred this site.
